{"tid":604260,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"成日覺得，90後係被遺忘嘅一代","createTime":"2018-03-24T13:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-30T12:56:04.000Z","uid":36467,"like":69,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"09001af6e9be9033d8fca7a524568e587e2146c2","tid":604260,"uid":36467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T13:53:35.000Z","msg":"當70,80後已經過咗30歲，開始被社會摧殘，接受咗命運;<br />\n90後啱啱進入社會，雖仍抱住一絲熱血，但係面對住香港最on9嘅10年。<br />\n<br />\n當00後心入面冇咗香港，去奶共，屌佔鐘;90後成為最後，亦係唯一一代寧死不屈嘅一代。<br />\n<br />\n當00後係被雙非侵佔嘅一代;90後係最後一班視香港為唯一一個屋企嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n當我地日日俾班老屎忽屌廢青，再望住00後明明都係後生仔但唔係同我地同聲同氣&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n唔知點解，我覺得90後好似先係唔屬於呢個社會嘅一班人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9edff3d09158badd67a80fc2def20c27c9198d0","tid":604260,"uid":29702,"like":5,"dislike":8,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T13:56:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"970f2a00c8ec75ef2baaa2548c1927234ec0e35f","tid":604260,"uid":4525,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T13:58:07.000Z","msg":"你班垃圾真係好煩<br />\n日撚日都無病呻吟"},{"pid":"61e67707c96f8786e6a277af02aa6fda746e80a9","tid":604260,"uid":176451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T14:14:43.000Z","msg":"sad but true<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bebbf24475f719e9bec80063142561743d3d8b","tid":604260,"uid":19028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"970f2a00c8ec75ef2baaa2548c1927234ec0e35f","tid":604260,"uid":4525,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T13:58:07.000Z","msg":"你班垃圾真係好煩<br />\n日撚日都無病呻吟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T14:16:24.000Z","msg":"關你撚事咩屌你老母"},{"pid":"93afb0514895cc39378224d7ba16fd05c9059a75","tid":604260,"uid":145126,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"970f2a00c8ec75ef2baaa2548c1927234ec0e35f","tid":604260,"uid":4525,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T13:58:07.000Z